  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] This is at the time of the-- [BACKGROUND NOISE] can you cut this off?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You want me to--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Say that again.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, Harvard Law School was a, a very great discipline.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I nearly didn't survive the first year.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But after that, I learned how to beat the system, and I got good notebooks from other, from other students who were a year ahead of me, and-- because I hated going to the long classes.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I only attended about half the classes in Harvard.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's how it went.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think I better answer that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It may be something--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I didn't particularly enjoy it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was very glad-- actually, my-- I got involved in the moot court arguments.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was in the Powell Club.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And professor Thomas Reed Powell was the person we honored.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we would, now and then, have meetings with him, with beer and without.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was very friendly to us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] That club won the Ames Competition that year, which was the moot court arguments.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it happened to involve a case which was about to be decided by the Supreme Court.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I forget the name of it now, but I can give you a copy or show you a copy in the next room.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because it's all bound up because of the fact that we won, and so on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It involved a labor case which was before the United States Supreme Court.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And our briefs were actually used by the Department of Justice later in part of their preparations.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because we had spent a great deal of time and developed materials that they thought were helpful to them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I took those briefs and came down to Washington after I graduated from Harvard Law School.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
